{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1158597, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把“不打疫苗”改成“不戴口罩”就理解了", "timestamp": 1614483755, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158598, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "selection bias", "timestamp": 1614483773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158601, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不带口罩是违反政府条例的，政府条例也是中国法律体系的一部分", "timestamp": 1614483802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 口罩理论上还是强制的，但实际课堂、图书馆很多人不戴，何况疫苗不是自愿的", "timestamp": 1614483838, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: “公共场合应戴口罩”", "timestamp": 1614483840, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不是一码事吧", "timestamp": 1614483857, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158611, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 打错了，何况疫苗还是自愿的", "timestamp": 1614483874, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158617, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不过这个洞Alice让我对为什么会吵起来有点概念了hhh", "timestamp": 1614483920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是因为群体免疫需要一定比例的人接种。如果只有40%的人接了，60%不接，这40%的人约等于白接了。相当于这60%不接的人损害了40%的人的利益，而这60%的人认为接种疫苗损害自己利益。所以这里产生了矛盾，就吵起来了。如果80%的人接了，那剩下20%的人不会损害80%的人的利益，也就不会吵。问题是，根据树洞上的画风，看起来更像是前者。", "timestamp": 1614484065, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158655, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上面各位，我在解释为啥会吵好吧....", "timestamp": 1614484140, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158668, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: hhh确实", "timestamp": 1614484226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1158673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229013, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 无意冒犯，谢谢Alice以身饲虎（x）", "timestamp": 1614484250, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 229013, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "不大清楚为啥要吵疫苗？\n只要不违法不违规不被训诫就是自由的边界内有啥可吵的吗……\n还是说不打疫苗会面临类似yp出轨海王这些问题的树洞道德审判", "timestamp": 1614483710, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1614484251, "url": "", "vote": {}}}